item.dc:creator: @chris_lol chris lol
item.description:

ok go to run and type in cmd. then type ipconfig. get your ip adress. then go into your router, and make sure the last didgits are still the same in the port you made. sometimes if your computer restarts your ip changes and it dosent change in the port on your router.
